Bodrogkeresztúr (originally shortly "Keresztúr", Yiddish: קערעסטיר‎) is a village in Borsod-Abaúj-Zemplén county, Hungary.

People[edit]

  • Rebbe Yeshaya Steiner of Kerestir hasidic court, lived here
